<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(فَصْلٌ)</span> فِي الأَطْعِمَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَكُلُّ طَعَامٍ طَاهِرٍ)</span> لَا نَجِسٍ أَوْ مُتَنَجِّسٍ وَ <span class="c2">(لَا مَضَرَّةَ فِيهِ: حَلَالٌ، وَأَصْلُهُ الحِلُّ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَحَرُمَ نَجِسٌ كَدَمٍ، وَمَيْتَةٍ، وَ)</span> حَرُمَ <span class="c2">(مُضِرٌّ كَسُمٍّ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> حَرُمَ <span class="c2">(مِنْ حَيَوَانِ بَرٍّ: مَا يَفْتَرِسُ بِنَابِهِ؛ كَأَسَدٍ وَنَمِرٍ وَفَهْدٍ وَثَعْلَبٍ وَابْنِ آوَى)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(لَا)</span> يَحْرُمُ <span class="c2">(ضَبُعٌ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> حَرُمَ <span class="c2">(مِنْ طَيْرٍ: مَا يَصِيدُ بِمِخْلَبٍ كَعُقَابٍ وَصَقْرٍ، وَ)</span> حَرُمَ مِنَ طَيْرٍ <span class="c2">(مَا يَأْكُلُ الجِيَفَ؛ كَنَسْرٍ وَرَخَمٍ)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> حَرُمَ كُلُّ <span class="c2">(مَا تَسْتَخْبِثُهُ العَرَبُ ذَوُو اليَسَارِ؛ كَوَطْوَاطٍ وَقُنْفُذٍ ونَيْصٍ)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> حَرُمَ <span class="c2">(مَا تَوَلَّدَ مِنْ مَأْكُولٍ وَغَيْرِهِ؛ كَبَغْلٍ)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(وَيُبَاحُ حَيَوَانُ بَحْرٍ كُلُّهُ؛<span class="c5"> سِوَى:</span> ضِفْدِعٍ، وَتِمْسَاحٍ، وَحَيَّةٍ)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(وَمَنِ اُضْطُرَّ)</span> بِأَنْ خَافَ التَّلَفَ إِنْ لَمْ يَأْكُلْ: <span class="c2">(أَكَلَ وُجُوبًا مِنْ مُحَرَّمٍ - غَيْرَ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>سُمٍّ - مَا يَسُدُّ رَمَقَهُ).<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(وَيَلْزَمُ مُسْلِمًا ضِيَافَةُ مُسْلِمٍ مُسَافِرٍ)</span> لَا مُقِيمٍ <span class="c2">(فِي قَرْيَةٍ لَا)</span> فِي <span class="c2">(مِصْرٍ يَوْمًا وَلَيْلَةً قَدْرَ كِفَايَتِهِ، وَتُسَنُّ)</span> الضِّيَافَةُ <span class="c2">(ثَلَاثَةَ أَيَّامٍ)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(فَصْلٌ)</span> فِي الذَّكَاةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(لَا يُبَاحُ حَيَوَانٌ يَعِيشُ فِي البَرِّ - غَيْرَ جَرَادٍ وَنَحْوِهِ -)</span> كَجُنْدُبٍ <span class="c2">(إِلَّا بِذَكَاةٍ)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(وَشُرُوطُهَا)</span> أَيِ الذَّكَاةِ <span class="c2">(أَرْبَعَةٌ)</span>:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">أَحَدُهَا:</span> <span class="c2">(كَوْنُ ذَابِحٍ: عَاقِلًا، مُمَيِّزًا وَلَوْ)</span> كَانَ <span class="c2">(كِتَابِيًّا)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>